What is a Lovlas Number?
Your Lovlas Number is the shortest chain of opponents connecting you to lovlas, a Lichess4545 legend who played in seasons 1-15.

If you played someone who played lovlas directly, your number is 2.
The lower your number, the closer you are to league history!
